(4,"fr_FR","Peut se décrire, décrire ce qu'il/elle fait, ainsi que son lieu d'habitation"),
(5,"en_US","CAN ask simple questions of a factual nature and understand the answers provided these are expressed in simple language (for example, 'Where is the dining-room?' 'It's on the first floor', etc.)"),
